    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.12.40"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">40</fw>
                
                <fw type="letterhead">
                    <hi rend="caps">LOUIS BROMFIELD
                
                    25, BOULEVARD FLANDRIN, XVII
                        <lb/>
                    AUTEUIL</hi> 42-13
                </fw>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>25th November 1926.</dateline>
                
                    <dateline>Dear Mr. Neihardt,</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Just a line to explain the long delay in answering your note of November 3rd.</p>
                
                <p>It was sent to Cold Spring Harbour, thense to Stokes', my Publisihers, and finally, to me here in Paris, so that it only reached me yesterday.</p>
                
                <p>I shall be delighted to answer the question you asked, and will send you the answer within a day or two. I shall take care not to make it too long. I have asked Stokes to forward you a photograph.</p> 
                
                <p>I was very much interested in learning that you are the Literary Editor of "<hi rend="caps">POST DISPATCG<sic>DISPATCH</sic></hi>".</p>
                
                <p>I take it that you are John Neihardt, the poet, whose work I have admired for a long time.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>With the best of wishes,</salute> 
                    <salute>I am,</salute>
                    <salute>Yours sincerely,</salute> 
                
                    <signed>Louis Bromfield</signed>
                
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>John Neihardt, Esq.,</addrLine>
                            <addrLine>Literary Editor,</addrLine>
                                <addrLine><hi rend="caps">ST. LOUIS POST-DISPATCH,</hi></addrLine>
                                    <addrLine>S t.  L o u i s.</addrLine>
                    </address>
                </closer>
              
            </div1>
        </body>
        
